data.description: SELLER IS GIVING 5K IN CONCESSIONS FOR CARPET AND PAINT. Exceptional 3 bedroom, 2 full bath, 1 living area home. Great floor plan! Open concept with charming large living area and great laminate wood flooring. Opens to wonderful eat-in kitchen making entertaining a delight. Kitchen has laminate countertops and stainless steel appliances. Lovely primary suite and large bath is perfect for relaxing. Huge backyard with open patio for outdoor living. Home is located near Fort Elementary and Royse City High School as well as I-30 for your convenience. Community has greenbelt, pool access, and play park. UPDATE* No leaseback will be needed!
